# Templates Directory

This directory stores saved templates as JSON files.
Each template is saved with its UUID as the filename.

## Structure

```
templates/
├── .gitkeep
├── {template-uuid-1}.json
├── {template-uuid-2}.json
└── ...
```

## Template Format

Templates are stored in JSON format with the following structure:

```json
{
  "id": "uuid",
  "name": "Template Name",
  "front": {
    "html": "<div>...</div>",
    "components": [...]
  },
  "back": {
    "html": "<div>...</div>",
    "components": [...]
  },
  "css": "/* shared styles */",
  "noteType": "Basic",
  "createdAt": "2026-01-31T12:00:00",
  "modifiedAt": "2026-01-31T12:00:00",
  "version": 1
}
```
